init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look down and see a bee in a suit and tie.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm not going to sting you, Your Majesty," the bee said.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm here to help you with your duties as a queen," the bee said.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They said I was the only one who could save them from the evil queen who was trying to take over the hive.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I agreed to be their queen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I had to go through a lot of obstacles to get to her, but I was determined to save my hive.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The third obstacle was a giant tree.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The third obstacle was a giant snake.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She had a crown on her head and a scepter in her hand.
